Interface IClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivityReportController, AssessorScreenController, DirectorHomePageController, EmployeesDataController, ExaminerScreenController, ExecutorScreenController, ExternHomePageController, HomePageController, LogInController, MyRequestController, MyRequestDirectorController, NotificationController, RequestsDataController, ReviewAssessmentScreenController, SubmitNewRequestController, SubmitNewRequestDirectorController, SupervisorScreenController, UserInformationController, UserInformationDirectorController

    public interface IClient
    Every GUI Controller that need to get messages from server, will have to implement this interface. Help us to route the messages from server and to identify the user logged in.
